{"tid":1037333,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易休戰】特朗普: 中美非常接近達成貿易協議","createTime":"2019-02-26T00:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T04:55:25.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88448aa0e8d5e3e0b1906d9b71a8346e611dbf0c","tid":1037333,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:53:40.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，中美雙方談判「非常、非常接近」達成協議 ; 他計劃同中國國家主席習近平舉行峰會，簽署貿易協議。<br />\n特朗普在白宮同州長會面時說，中美短期內很可能達成協議，但亦有可能不成事。<br />\n特朗普稍早前宣布，將延長原定於3月1日實施向總值二千億美元中國貨加徵關稅的期限，他亦打算與習近平在佛羅里達海湖莊園會晤期間簽署協議。"},{"pid":"162f36bd9d9a1385b916385fdfea642504e17c1f","tid":1037333,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:56:17.000Z","msg":"千升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0cfa87fc79a5c135cd1d150fc8ae9ac54ffbb0","tid":1037333,"uid":63108,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"呢個新聞好似睇左幾十次咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dad2c2352558b8fd00bd5bd1e5d748c87345bc","tid":1037333,"uid":217096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"千跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e707373122a8f7d9d6c522804e8c8b0600d89e9e","tid":1037333,"uid":18811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:02:46.000Z","msg":"接近都講咗幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444b73690e29f088b6d0bad79b3e2825fd7b0891","tid":1037333,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:05:14.000Z","msg":"短期內很可能達成協議，但亦有可能不成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a584ad3391f500d61e135209ad409c625bc1b54","tid":1037333,"uid":60376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"硬係形住佢講緊反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":